Name: The Power of Many Website
Description: Say we want to guess the number of jelly beans in a jar. The chances of one person’s guess being right is very slim. However, if we ask many people and take the average, our new guess will be highly accurate. We are trying to create a platform to harness the power of many for any seemingly small task, yet difficult for one person.
